text: Phylograms obtained for the core group from the character based algorithms ProtPars [ 4 ] and ProtML [ 4 ] are shown in the additional files 4 and 5 , while phylograms obtained from the two distance - based algorithms are shown in the additional files 6 and 7 . The phylogram obtained by Mr . Bayes [ 7 ] is displayed in Figure 6 . P18269Sial , a trypanosoan sialdase and Q05JH9H9N2 , a NA of the distantly related H9N2 virus have been used as members of an outlier group for the phyloinformatics analysis .
